OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fmostly clear eastwards overnight,
OL,7,Falthough it will remain largely
OL,8,Fcloudy. A chance of isolated showers
OL,9,Fovernight. Some clearer spells may
OL,10,Fdevelop towards dawn. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,13,Fcloud and sunny spells expected for
OL,14,Fmuch of the day, though a few light
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain are possible at
OL,16,Ftimes. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
