OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry through this period with
OL,7,Fpatchy cloud and sunny spells. Breezy
OL,8,Fon Saturday but winds falling light
OL,9,Ffor Sunday and Monday. Feeling warm,
OL,10,Fespecially in the sunshine.
